OL,3,CThird arrest made after boy, 16,
OL,4,Cseriously injured in Bournemouth
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FDorset Police have arrested a third
OL,8,Fperson after a 16-year-old boy was
OL,9,Fseriously injured in Bournemouth.
OL,11,FOfficers received a report at 7.18pm
OL,12,Fon Sunday 26 April 2026 that a 16-year-
OL,13,Fold boy had been assaulted in the area
OL,14,Fof Maclean Road.
OL,16,FPolice said the victim had suffered
OL,17,Fsuspected stab wounds.
OL,19,FHe was taken to hospital for treatment
OL,20,Fto serious injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
