OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778166668
OL,3,CThird arrest made after boy, 16,
OL,4,Cseriously injured in Bournemouth
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FA 17-year-old boy from Poole and a 17-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy from Bournemouth were
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of inflicting
OL,10,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent and
OL,11,Fwere released on police bail.
OL,13,FFollowing further investigations, a 20-
OL,14,Fyear-old man from Bournemouth was also
OL,15,Farrested on suspicion of inflicting
OL,16,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent.
OL,18,FHe has also been released on police
OL,19,Fbail as enquiries continue.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
