OL,3,CThird arrest made after boy, 16,
OL,4,Cseriously injured in Bournemouth
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FA cordon was put in place to allow
OL,8,Fpolice to carry out an examination of
OL,9,Fthe scene.
OL,11,FAnybody with information is being
OL,12,Fasked to contact Dorset Police online
OL,13,For by calling 101 and quoting the
OL,14,Fnumber 55260059619.
OL,16,FThe independent charity Crimestoppers
OL,17,Fcan also be contacted anonymously.
